ule to incorporate the queue-based verification system, replacing the old `stats1` logic for mismatches, while preserving the overall structure and the `stimulus_gen`/`RefModule` interaction.\n3.  Update the final check in `tb` to use the queue mismatch count/time, adhering strictly to the required final display format.",
